- 她朝着它笔直飞过去了
- 没错
- She's heading straight for it.
- On my mark.

668
01:11:37,857 --> 01:11:39,415
- 她准备撞它了
- 这是自杀啊
- She's going to ram it.
- It's suicide.

669
01:11:39,625 --> 01:11:41,490
弗兰基,拉起来
Franky, pull up.

670
