快点！
Come on!

690
01:15:35,928 --> 01:15:36,829
你疯了吗？
Are you mad?

691
01:15:36,829 --> 01:15:37,659
你是不是疯了？
Are you mad?

692
01:15:37,863 --> 01:15:42,027
你脑子是不是有毛病？
刚才你差点就害得自己被杀掉了！
Are you completely insane?
You could have gotten yourself killed!

693
01:15:47,006 --> 01:15:49,406
- 算了算了
- 哦，没关系
- It's okay.
- No, it isn't.

694
01:15:49,609 --> 01:15:51,907
- 我的意思不是
- 我刚才拍的是地面！
- I didn't mean--
- I shot the ground!

695
01:15:54,447 --> 01:15:55,971
- 什么？
- 当我们在逃跑的时候
- What?
- When we were running,

696
01:15:56,182 --> 01:15:59,083
我拍了地面
I shot the ground.

697
01:16:03,656 --> 01:16:05,556
这个一点也不好笑
It isn't funny.

698
01:16:07,593 --> 01:16:12,690
我只剩下一张底片了
一张！
I only have one shot left.
One shot!

699
01:16:19,572 --> 01:16:22,439
那个鬼相机对你来说有什么意义？
What is it with you
and that stupid camera, anyway?

700
01:16:23,042 --> 01:16:24,532
是你送给我的
You gave it to me.

701
01:16:27,613 --> 01:16:29,240
连你自己也不记得了？
You don't even remember, do you?

702
01:16:30,650 --> 01:16:33,141
当你和美国志愿者在南京开着飞机的时候
You were flying with the American
volunteers in Nanjing,

703
01:16:33,352 --> 01:16:35,912
我正在报道上海的撤退
I was covering the evacuation
of Shanghai.

704
01:16:36,455 --> 01:16:38,252
- 我记得的
- 约瑟夫，我想问你几个问题
- I remember.
- Joe, I wanna ask you something

705
01:16:38,457 --> 01:16:39,856
你得老实回答我的问题
and I want you to tell me the truth.

706
01:16:40,092 --> 01:16:43,926
我发誓我不在乎答案是什么
我只是想知道真相
I don't care one way or the other,
I swear. I just need to know.

707
01:16:44,563 --> 01:16:46,224
你在南京的女友是弗兰基
对吗？
The girl in Nanjing was Franky,
wasn't it?

708
01:16:46,432 --> 01:16:49,458
- 波莉
- 你和她在一起呆了多久？
- Polly.
- How long were you seeing her?

709
01:16:51,170 --> 01:16:52,228
看着我的眼睛
Look me in the eyes.

710
01:16:53,806 --> 01:16:56,240
我从来没有让你戴过绿帽子
I never fooled around on you.

711
01:16:56,442 --> 01:16:57,409
从来没有
Never.

712
01:17:00,346 --> 01:17:02,246
是我破坏了你的飞机
I sabotaged your plane.

713
01:17:04,250 --> 01:17:05,774
- 三个月
- 我就知道！
- Three months.
- I knew it!

714
01:17:05,985 --> 01:17:08,818
我不敢想象我怎么才能相信你
你这个可恶的
I can't believe I ever trusted you,
you lousy--

715
01:17:13,492 --> 01:17:15,187
他在这里
He's here.

716
01:17:26,038 --> 01:17:27,733
你没事吧？
You all right?

717
01:17:43,622 --> 01:17:44,987
从这里走
Through there.

718
01:17:51,731 --> 01:17:52,698
从这里走
Through there.

719
01:18:53,259 --> 01:18:54,658
我的天啊，约瑟夫
My God, Joe.

720
01:18:55,995 --> 01:18:57,656
是诺亚方舟
It's an ark.

721
01:18:57,863 --> 01:19:00,195
他在建一个诺亚方舟
He's building an ark.

722
01:19:10,309 --> 01:19:12,004
你在干嘛？
What are you doing?

723
01:19:14,013 --> 01:19:16,675
你认为还有比把地球上所有的
You honestly think you're gonna
find something more important

724
01:19:16,882 --> 01:19:20,010
生物成双成对的
放在这个巨大的火箭船里面
than every single creature on Earth
being led two by two

725
01:19:20,219 --> 01:19:22,551
更为壮观的场景吗？
inside a giant rocket ship?

726
01:19:23,155 --> 01:19:24,782
我也许还能发现更壮观的
I might.

727
01:19:26,292 --> 01:19:28,817
- 比如说？
- 当我看见的时候就知道了
- Like what?
- I'll know when I see it.

728
01:19:37,870 --> 01:19:40,600
- 离起飞还有10分钟
- 他们开始倒计时了
- Ten minutes to liftoff.
- They've started the countdown.

729
01:19:40,806 --> 01:19:43,206
我们得找到托滕可夫
We have to find Totenkopf.

730
01:19:52,918 --> 01:19:54,579
这下你中奖了
You've got a gift.

731
01:20:20,112 --> 01:20:21,739
- 德克斯！
- 快点，进来！
- Dex!
- Hurry, get in!

732
01:20:26,652 --> 01:20:27,812
上来
科姆，快走！
Einsteigen. Komm, springt!

733
01:20:35,361 --> 01:20:36,919
你们都还好吧？
你怎么找到我们的？
Are you all right?
How did you find us?

734
01:20:37,129 --> 01:20:39,188
倒计时开始的时候我们逃进了隧道
We escaped into the tunnels
once the countdown started.

735
01:20:39,398 --> 01:20:42,026
还有一些科学家没能逃出来
Some of the scientists were caught.
They didn't make it.

736
01:20:44,870 --> 01:20:46,167
看守我们的那些机器人
The machines that were guarding us

737
01:20:46,372 --> 01:20:48,340
正在把这个岛上的所有东西装上船
are loading everything on this island
into that ship.

738
01:20:48,540 --> 01:20:50,838
我们只有大约十分钟时间来阻止
飞船点火起飞
We've got about ten minutes
to stop that thing from blasting off.

739
01:20:53,479 --> 01:20:55,879
德克斯！ 带我们离开这里！
Dex! Get us out of here!

740
01:21:19,204 --> 01:21:20,569
干得好，德克斯
Good boy, Dex.

741
01:21:21,473 --> 01:21:22,735
谢谢，上尉
Thanks, Cap.

742
01:21:27,279 --> 01:21:29,076
- 他们是谁？
- 他们是11单元
- Who are they?
- They're Unit 1 1.

743
01:21:29,281 --> 01:21:30,373
也可以说是11单元的幸存者
Or what's left of them.

744
01:21:30,582 --> 01:21:33,608
他们被带到这里完成一个30年前的计划
They were brought here to finish
what they started 30 years ago.

745
01:21:33,819 --> 01:21:35,081
完成什么？
Finish what?

746
01:21:35,454 --> 01:21:36,421
告诉他们
Tell them.

747
01:21:36,622 --> 01:21:39,682
托滕可夫认为人类注定要灭亡
Totenkopf believed that humankind
was doomed to extinction,

748
01:21:39,892 --> 01:21:41,519
所以他不可思议的提出了：
so he proposed the unthinkable:

749
01:21:41,727 --> 01:21:45,163
建造一个装置把另外一个文明所需的
基础单元
To build a vessel that would carry
the building blocks of a new civilization

750
01:21:45,364 --> 01:21:46,331
送入太空
into space.

751
01:21:46,532 --> 01:21:48,523
他利用他的机器人
He used his machines
to collect specimens

752
01:21:48,734 --> 01:21:50,395
把地球上的所有物种放在一起
representing all life on Earth.

753
01:21:50,602 --> 01:21:52,194
托滕可夫称之为“明日帝国”
What Totenkopf called
"The World of Tomorrow."

754
01:21:52,404 --> 01:21:55,202
詹宁斯博士给我的那些管子是什么？
Those vials that Dr. Jennings
gave me, what were they?

755
01:21:55,407 --> 01:21:57,705
亚当和夏娃
托滕可夫的杰作
Adam and Eve.
Totenkopf's masterpiece.

756
01:21:57,910 --> 01:22:00,174
科技乌托邦的星星之火
Seeds of a technological utopia.

757
01:22:00,379 --> 01:22:01,778
我们偷偷的把他们带出了这个小岛
We smuggled them off this island,

758
01:22:01,981 --> 01:22:03,778
因为我们知道托滕可夫没有他们
是不会离开的
knowing Totenkopf
would never leave without them.

759
01:22:03,983 --> 01:22:07,544
