01:25:47,306 --> 01:25:48,933
他20年前就死了
He died over 20 years ago.

806
01:25:55,814 --> 01:25:57,611
我们一直在寻找一个幽灵
We've been chasing a ghost.

807
01:26:10,329 --> 01:26:12,763
还有3分钟时间起飞
Three minutes to liftoff.

808
01:26:18,837 --> 01:26:21,305
没有办法阻止他们了
他们正在按照程序完成整个计划
They never stopped. They're finishing
what they were programmed to do.

809
01:26:21,506 --> 01:26:26,876
你难道没看见？整个岛就是托滕可夫
每根管线，每套设备
Don't you see? This entire island
is Totenkopf. Every wire, every gear.

810
01:26:27,079 --> 01:26:30,048
连他的死也是在欺骗我们
He's found a way to cheat
even his own death.

811
01:26:30,249 --> 01:26:33,241
我们怎么杀死一个已经死了的人？
So how do we kill somebody
who's already dead?

812
01:26:35,320 --> 01:26:37,049
- 我怎样才能阻止它？
- 现在没有任何东西能够阻止它了
- How do I stop it?
- Nothing can stop it now.

813
01:26:37,256 --> 01:26:39,622
- 一定有什么办法
- 他的机器人不会允许你这么做的
- There must be some way.
- His machines would never allow it.

814
01:26:39,825 --> 01:26:42,157
我来解决这些机器人
德克斯，告诉我怎么做
Leave the machines to me.
Dex, show me what to do.

815
01:26:45,130 --> 01:26:47,690
如果你切断系统终端的导航部分
If you can cut the lead
in the system terminal,

816
01:26:47,899 --> 01:26:50,197
会引起短路...
it should create a short...

817
01:26:51,870 --> 01:26:54,998
可以在助推发动机点火前
点燃燃料管线
...which will ignite the fuel line
before the booster engines can fire

818
01:26:55,207 --> 01:26:56,970
- 来破坏发动机点火的气氛
- 就这样？
- and destroy the atmosphere.
- That's it?

819
01:26:58,510 --> 01:27:01,877
- 这就是我所要做的？
- 但是终端在飞船上面
- That's all I have to do?
- The terminal's onboard the rocket.

820
01:27:02,080 --> 01:27:04,412
你将没有时间逃离
You won't have time to escape.

821
01:27:07,819 --> 01:27:09,980
你们离开这个岛后
马上和弗兰基取得联系
Contact Franky as soon
as you're off the island.

822
01:27:10,188 --> 01:27:12,952
- 她知道该怎么办
- 你们在讲些什么？
- She'll know exactly what to do.
- What are you talking about?

823
01:27:13,158 --> 01:27:15,683
- 我要和你一起去
- 这次不行
- I'm going with you.
- Not this time.

824
01:27:15,894 --> 01:27:17,885
我们说好了的
We had a deal.

825
01:27:18,563 --> 01:27:21,589
你不能在事情变得有趣的时候离开我
You're not gonna leave me now,
just when things are getting interesting.

826
01:27:24,569 --> 01:27:28,300
- 我不会让你一个人走的
- 我希望我们要是有更多时间就好了
- I won't let you.
- I wish we had more time.

827
01:27:28,507 --> 01:27:31,670
现在我只是希望，有那么一天
你能原谅我
And I only hope, one day,
you can forgive me.

828
01:27:40,619 --> 01:27:43,087
- 照顾好她，德克斯
- 祝你好运，上尉
- Take care of her, Dex.
- Good luck, Cap.

829
01:27:50,662 --> 01:27:53,062
一分钟后起飞
One minute to liftoff.

830
01:28:07,446 --> 01:28:09,539
我们又见面了
我神秘的朋友
We meet again,
my mysterious friend.

831
01:28:12,851 --> 01:28:13,875
你要怎么样？
How do you wanna do this?

832
01:29:21,720 --> 01:29:23,950
干得好,波莉
Nice shot, Polly.

833
01:29:34,332 --> 01:29:36,493
你怎么这么久才来？
What took you so long?

834
01:29:40,872 --> 01:29:42,032
她是机器人
She's a machine.

835
01:29:49,247 --> 01:29:51,875
10秒后起飞
Ten seconds to liftoff.

836
01:30:50,976 --> 01:30:52,739
我们得把这些动物弄下飞船
We've gotta get those animals
off the ship.

837
01:30:52,944 --> 01:30:55,139
90公里后发动机点火
Ninety kilometers to booster ignition.

838
01:30:55,347 --> 01:30:56,609
没时间了
There's no time.

839
01:31:01,052 --> 01:31:02,576
这是我们过去的唯一途径
That's our only way across.

840
01:31:07,392 --> 01:31:09,860
80公里后发动机点火
Eighty kilometers to booster ignition.

841
01:31:19,037 --> 01:31:22,598
危险！危险！危险！
飞船货物即将卸下！
Danger! Danger! Danger!
Cargo release imminent!

842
01:31:23,074 --> 01:31:24,769
你刚才做什么了？
What did you do now?

843
01:31:29,047 --> 01:31:30,014
快来！
Come on!

844
01:31:30,215 --> 01:31:32,843
70公里后发动机点火
Seventy kilometers to booster ignition.

845
01:31:45,764 --> 01:31:47,664
60公里后发动机点火
Sixty kilometers to booster ignition.

846
01:31:50,902 --> 01:31:52,494
抓牢！
Hold on!

847
01:31:59,244 --> 01:32:02,975
天啊！不要再碰任何东西了！
Please! Don't touch anything else!

848
01:32:11,156 --> 01:32:13,647
没时间了，我们无法阻止它了
There's no time. We'll never make it.

849
01:32:14,793 --> 01:32:17,557
50公里后发动机点火
Fifty kilometers to booster ignition.

850
01:32:25,303 --> 01:32:26,327
快跑！
Run!

851
01:32:27,806 --> 01:32:30,206
40公里后发动机点火
Forty kilometers to booster ignition.

852
01:32:37,949 --> 01:32:40,247
请求进入，曼塔基地
你收到我的消息了吗？
Come in, Manta station.
Do you read me?

853
01:32:42,787 --> 01:32:45,654
30公里后发动机点火
Thirty kilometers to booster ignition.

854
01:32:49,794 --> 01:32:51,989
弗兰基，我是德克斯
你能收到我的消息吗？
Franky, it's Dex. Do you read me?

855
01:33:01,272 --> 01:33:02,239
这样没用
It didn't work.

856
01:33:05,810 --> 01:33:07,778
20公里后发动机点火
Twenty kilometers to booster ignition.

857
01:33:08,380 --> 01:33:11,645
约瑟夫，你没时间了
你得想点办法
Joe, you're running out of time.
You've gotta do something.

858
01:33:13,184 --> 01:33:17,120
上帝看见地球上恶人横行
And God saw that the wickedness
of man was great in the earth...

859
01:33:17,322 --> 01:33:20,257
- 他以为自己是上帝
- 上帝告诉诺亚，末日...
- He thinks he's God.
- And God said unto Noah, the end...

860
01:33:20,458 --> 01:33:21,755
住嘴！
Shut up!

861
01:33:21,960 --> 01:33:24,554
10公里后发动机点火
Ten kilometers to booster ignition.

862
01:33:30,201 --> 01:33:32,761
- 6
- 你怎么还不去死？
-...six...
- Why won't you die?

863
01:33:32,971 --> 01:33:35,098
5公里后发动机点火
Five kilometers to booster ignition.

864
01:33:49,454 --> 01:33:51,752
警告，系统故障
Warning. System failure.

865
01:33:52,157 --> 01:33:53,784
发动机故障
Booster malfunction.

866
01:33:53,992 --> 01:33:56,051
危险，危险
Danger. Danger.

867
01:33:56,261 --> 01:33:57,421
危险
Danger.

868
01:33:57,629 --> 01:34:00,154
警告，系统故障
Warning. System failure.

869
01:34:00,365 --> 01:34:01,593
- 发动机故障
- 小心！
- Booster malfunction.
- Look!

870
01:34:01,900 --> 01:34:03,265
危险，危险
Danger. Danger.

871
01:34:03,468 --> 01:34:06,232
- 这是什么？
- 也许是我们的逃生之路
- What is it?
- It might be our way out of here.

872
01:34:23,988 --> 01:34:25,922
我看见他们了，长官
I see them, commander.

873
01:34:26,424 --> 01:34:30,383
攻击分队预备
所有船员做好准备
Ready assault teams.
All hands on deck.

874
01:35:22,480 --> 01:35:24,311
最后一张
One shot.

875
01:35:27,418 --> 01:35:29,147
你得到了你的新闻了
You got your story.

876
01:35:46,905 --> 01:35:48,429
波莉
Polly.

877
01:35:49,941 --> 01:35:50,908
- 你...
- 没关系
- You...
- It's all right.

878
01:35:51,109 --> 01:35:53,373
你不需要说什么
You don't have to say anything.

879
01:35:56,114 --> 01:35:57,877
你的相机盖没有开
Lens cap.


